reviewText: Awesome movie. Great actors . Great story. Wholesome entertainment.
The movie starts of slow, and at some point can get a little boring for the first 30 odd minutes but then slowly picks up and starts getting interesting with good humor and interesting twists.
Parents really liked the movie, they laughed a lot. It was a good quality DVD and there were no problems shipping.
One of the funniest movie of 2011 from Bollywood. I have watched this movie several times and I never got bored of it.
